Installation:
This PC -> Documents -> My Games -> Skyrim -> CME_Save [place file here]
Rename file if already used
example: "_14_commonTriRaces" -> "_15_commonTriRaces" (no quotations)

Check credits for requirements :3
Please leave a comment if you have any problems, ideas, requests or complements.
Enjoy!
